-General of NUNW (1997-1998); District Coordinator of Namibia Food and Allied Union (NAFAU) (1988-1991); Clerk, Hanekom G. J. &amp; CO Chartered Accountants (1982-1984); Post Master (1985-1988); Part-time English Teacher (1984-1985).<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interests<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Not available<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Deputy Minister: Labour, Industrial Relations and Employment Creation SWAPO Party Legislative Profile Member of the National Council for Erongo Region (2001 &#8211; 2010); Member of the National Council\u2019s Standing Committee on Defence, Security and Foreign Affairs; Member of CPA Namibia Branch. Councilor for the Walvis Bay Urban Constituency. Personal Born, 10 October 1962 at Walvis&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2387,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","dt_team_category":[107,109,92],"class_list":["post-2386","dt_team","type-dt_team","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","dt_team_category-2nd-national-council-1998-2004","dt_team_category-3rd-national-council-2004-2010","dt_team_category-7th-national-assembly-2020-2025","dt_team_category-107","dt_team_category-109","dt_team_category-92","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team\/2386","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/dt_team"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2386"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2387"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2386"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"dt_team_category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team_category?pos